               <p>WILLIAM SMITH. This jacket is my property - it had been hanging in the passage of my house at <placeName id="t18260406-140-crimeloc742">Blackwall</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18260406-140-crimeloc742" type="placeName" value="Blackwall"></interp>
